{"name":"React","postlist":[{"title":"React","slug":"recat","date":"2021-03-18T11:29:18.000Z","updated":"2021-06-01T09:35:08.902Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/recat.json","excerpt":null,"keywords":null,"cover":"C:\\Users\\梁超\\AppData\\Roaming\\Typora\\typora-user-images\\image-20210601145738404.png","content":"<h4 id=\"什么是-React\"><a href=\"#什么是-React\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"什么是 React ?\"></a>什么是 React ?</h4><p>  React是一个声明式的，高效的，并且灵活的<strong>用于构建用户界面的 JavaScript 库</strong></p>\n<p>React特点：</p>\n<p><strong>1声明式</strong>：你只需要描述UI（HTML）看起来是什么样，就和写HTML一样React负责渲染UI，并在数据变化时更新UI</p>\n<p><strong>2基于组件</strong>：</p>\n<p>组件是React<strong>最重要</strong>的内容</p>\n<p>组件表示页面中的部分内容</p>\n<p>组合、复用多个组件，可以实现完整页面功能</p>\n<p><strong>3学习一次，随处使用</strong></p>\n<p>使用React可以开发Web应用</p>\n<p>使用React可以开发移动端原生应用（react-native）</p>\n<p>使用React可以开发VR（虚拟现实）应用（react 360）</p>\n<h5 id=\"React安装：-npm-i-react-react-dom\"><a href=\"#React安装：-npm-i-react-react-dom\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"React安装：  npm i react react-dom\"></a>React安装：  npm i react react-dom</h5><p><img src=\"C:\\Users\\梁超\\AppData\\Roaming\\Typora\\typora-user-images\\image-20210601145738404.png\" alt=\"image-20210601145738404\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"C:\\Users\\梁超\\AppData\\Roaming\\Typora\\typora-user-images\\image-20210601150716289.png\" alt=\"image-20210601150716289\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"C:\\Users\\梁超\\AppData\\Roaming\\Typora\\typora-user-images\\image-20210601150251211.png\"><img src=\"C:\\Users\\梁超\\AppData\\Roaming\\Typora\\typora-user-images\\image-20210601150602687.png\" alt=\"image-20210601150602687\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"C:\\Users\\梁超\\AppData\\Roaming\\Typora\\typora-user-images\\image-20210601150922148.png\" alt=\"image-20210601150922148\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"C:\\Users\\梁超\\AppData\\Roaming\\Typora\\typora-user-images\\image-20210601151145892.png\" alt=\"image-20210601151145892\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"C:\\Users\\梁超\\AppData\\Roaming\\Typora\\typora-user-images\\image-20210601160522644.png\" alt=\"image-20210601160522644\"></p>\n<h5 id=\"组件：\"><a href=\"#组件：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"组件：\"></a>组件：</h5><figure class=\"highlight jsx\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs jsx\"><br><span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 函数组件</span><br><span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 普通</span><br><span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">Hellow</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>)</span>&#123;<br>  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> (<br>    &lt;div&gt;我是函数组件&lt;/div&gt;<br>  )<br>&#125;<br><br><span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 箭头</span><br><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> Hellow=<span class=\"hljs-function\">()=&gt;</span><span class=\"xml\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span>我是函数组件<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><br><br>ReactDOM.render(<span class=\"xml\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">Hellow</span>/&gt;</span></span>,<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">document</span>.getElementById(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;root&#x27;</span>))<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight jsx\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs jsx\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">//类组件</span><br><span class=\"hljs-comment\">//创建类组件</span><br><span class=\"hljs-class\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">Hellow</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">React</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title\">Component</span></span>&#123;<br>  render()&#123;<br>    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span>(<br>      &lt;div&gt;我是类组件&lt;/div&gt;<br>    )<br>  &#125;<br>&#125;<br>ReactDOM.render(<span class=\"xml\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">Hellow</span>/&gt;</span></span>,<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">document</span>.getElementById(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;root&#x27;</span>))<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h5 id=\"抽离组件到单独js文件\"><a href=\"#抽离组件到单独js文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"抽离组件到单独js文件\"></a>抽离组件到单独js文件</h5><figure class=\"highlight jsx\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs jsx\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">//Hellow.js</span><br><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;react&#x27;</span>;<br><br><span class=\"hljs-comment\">//创建组件</span><br><span class=\"hljs-class\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">Hellow</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">React</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title\">Component</span></span>&#123;<br>   render()&#123;<br>      <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> (<br>         &lt;div&gt;抽离类组件&lt;/div&gt;<br>      )<br>   &#125;<br>&#125;<br><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">default</span> Hellow<br><br><span class=\"hljs-comment\">//index.js</span><br><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> Hellow <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;./page/Hellow&#x27;</span><br><br>ReactDOM.render(<span class=\"xml\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">Hellow</span>/&gt;</span></span>,<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">document</span>.getElementById(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;root&#x27;</span>))<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h5 id=\"React-事件处理\"><a href=\"#React-事件处理\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"React 事件处理\"></a>React 事件处理</h5><figure class=\"highlight jsx\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs jsx\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">//类组件绑定事件</span><br><span class=\"hljs-class\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">Hellow</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">React</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title\">Component</span></span>&#123;<br>   handClick()&#123;<br>      <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">console</span>.log(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;我被点击了&#x27;</span>);<br>   &#125;<br>   render()&#123;<br>      <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> (<br>         &lt;button onClick=&#123;<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">this</span>.handClick&#125;&gt;点击&lt;/button&gt;<br>      )<br>   &#125;<br>&#125;<br><span class=\"hljs-comment\">//函数组件绑定事件</span><br><span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">Hellow</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>)</span>&#123;<br>   <span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">handClick</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>)</span>&#123;<br>            <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">console</span>.log(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;我被点击了&#x27;</span>);<br>         &#125;<br>   <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span>(<br>      &lt;button onClick=&#123;handClick&#125;&gt;点击&lt;/button&gt;<br>   )<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h5 id=\"React-事件对象\"><a href=\"#React-事件对象\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"React 事件对象\"></a>React 事件对象</h5><figure class=\"highlight jsx\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs jsx\"><span class=\"hljs-class\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">Hellow</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">React</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title\">Component</span></span>&#123;<br>   handClick(e)&#123;<br>      e.preventDefault();<br>      <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">console</span>.log(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;a标签被点击了&#x27;</span>);<br>   &#125;<br>   render()&#123;<br>      <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> (<br>        &lt;a href=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;http://baidu.cn&#x27;</span> onClick=&#123;<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">this</span>.handClick&#125;&gt;去百度&lt;/a&gt;<br>      )<br>   &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h5 id=\"React-有状态组件（类组件）和无状态组件（函数组件）\"><a href=\"#React-有状态组件（类组件）和无状态组件（函数组件）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"React 有状态组件（类组件）和无状态组件（函数组件）\"></a>React 有状态组件（类组件）和无状态组件（函数组件）</h5><p>状态：（state）即<strong>数据</strong></p>\n<p>函数组件没有自己的状态，<strong>只负责数据展示</strong>（静）</p>\n<p>类组件有自己的状态，<strong>负责更新UI</strong>，让页面“动”起来</p>\n","raw":null,"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"React","path":"api/tags/React.json"}]}]}